      • getMessage

        public java.lang.String[] getMessage()
        Do Not Remove, this is used for File-Engine to get message from the plugin. You can show message using "displayMessage(String caption, String message)"
        返回:
        String[2], the first string is caption, the second string is message.
        另请参阅:
        Plugin.displayMessage(String, String)

      • pollFromResultQueue

        public java.lang.String pollFromResultQueue()
        Do Not Remove, this is used for File-Engine to get results from the plugin You can add result using "addToResultQueue(String result)".
        返回:
        result
        另请参阅:
        Plugin.addToResultQueue(String)
